title: Merrilee Rush - Angel of the Morning (320)
description:
Merrilee Rush - Angel of the Morning (320)

Merrilee Rush is best known for her top ten single "Angel of the Morning" in 1968.  It went to number seven on the charts and won her a nomination for a Grammy award for best Contemporary Pop Female Vocalist of the year.
